2006-07-12  Marius Vollmer  <marius.vollmer@nokia.com>

	* apt-pkg/acquire-item.cc (pkgAcqMetaSig::pkgAcqMetaSig): Don't
	move old version into partial/, we need it as a backup in the case
	the acquiring fails.
